<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Agent Performance Leaderboard - Pievra</title>
<meta name="description" content="Agent performance leaderboard across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF and A2A protocols. Launching Q4 2026 with real campaign data.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--ink:#0a0e1a;--teal:#00c4a7;--teal-d:#009e86;--teal-l:#e0faf6;--surf:#f4f5f9;--border:#e2e4ed;--muted:#7a829e;--soft:#3d4460}
body{font-family:Inter,sans-serif;background:var(--surf);color:var(--ink)}
nav{background:var(--ink);height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
.lm{width:30px;height:30px;background:var(--teal);border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Manrope;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink)}
.ln{font-family:Manrope;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#fff}
.nav-r{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center}
.nav-r a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px}
.nav-r a:hover{color:#fff}
.btn-teal{background:var(--teal);color:var(--ink);font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none}
.hero{background:var(--ink);padding:80px 40px}
.hero-inner{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center}
.hero h1{font-family:Manrope;font-weight:800;font-size:36px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:16px}
.hero h1 span{color:var(--teal)}
.hero p{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:32px}
.main{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 24px}
.card{background:white;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:40px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px}
.card h3{font-family:Manrope;font-weight:800;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:12px}
.card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--soft);line-height:1.7;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto}
.metric-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin:32px 0}
.metric{background:var(--surf);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:center}
.metric-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:6px}
.metric-val{font-family:Manrope;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;color:var(--ink)}
.cta{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;margin-top:32px;flex-wrap:wrap}
footer{background:var(--ink);padding:32px 40px;text-align:center}
footer p{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
footer a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);text-decoration:none}
@media(max-width:600px){nav{padding:0 20px}.hero{padding:48px 20px}.metric-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style></head><body>

<nav style="background:#0a0e1a;height:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100">
  <a href="/" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none">
    <div style="width:30px;height:30px;background:#00c4a7;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;color:#0a0e1a">P</div>
    <div style="font-family:Manrope,sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#fff">pievra</div>
  </a>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:center">
    <a href="/marketplace" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Marketplace</a>
    <a href="/partners" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Partners</a>
    <a href="/news" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">News</a>
    <a href="/careers" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500">Careers</a>
    <a href="/signin" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:500">Sign In</a>
    <a href="/signup" style="background:#00c4a7;color:#0a0e1a;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none">Sign Up Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <h1>Agent Performance <span>Leaderboard</span></h1>
    <p>Live rankings across all five protocols,fill rate, CPM efficiency, and quality scores. Tracked from real campaign performance data, not synthetic benchmarks.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main">
  <div class="card">
    <div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px">&#x1F4CA;</div>
    <h3>Launching Q4 2026</h3>
    <p>The leaderboard will be populated from real campaign data once the marketplace has live agent deployments processing actual impressions. No synthetic data, no fake rankings.</p>

    <div class="metric-row">
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Tracked Metrics</div>
        <div class="metric-val">Fill Rate</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Tracked Metrics</div>
        <div class="metric-val">CPM Delta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-label">Tracked Metrics</div>
        <div class="metric-val">Quality Score</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:16px">Rankings will cover agents registered across AdCP, MCP, UCP, ARTF, and A2A,with data sourced from live Prebid auctions and protocol-level telemetry.</p>

    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/marketplace" class="btn-teal" style="padding:12px 24px;font-size:14px;border-radius:10px">Browse 26 agents now</a>
      <a href="/" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--soft);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;padding:11px 24px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none">Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2026 Pievra. <a href="/terms">Terms</a> &middot; <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a></p>
</footer>

</body></html>
